# Pre-commit leak-scan denylist - EXAMPLE / template.
#
# Copy this to .githooks/leak-patterns.local (which is gitignored and never committed)
# and fill it with your real customer/portal tokens. The pre-commit hook blocks any
# commit whose staged ADDED lines match any pattern here.
#
# Format: one case-insensitive extended-regex (grep -E) per line. A plain word works as
# a substring match. Blank lines and lines starting with # are ignored.
#
# Bypass a genuine false positive once with:  LEAK_SCAN_SKIP=1 git commit ...
#
# --- examples (replace with your own in leak-patterns.local; do NOT put real ones here) ---
# acmecorp
# acme-portal
# 203\.0\.113\.
# 198\.51\.100\.
# [a-z]+prod[0-9]{2}
